topics.body:
So I was actually late to my Anatomy exam.

This school is so annoying with its schedule, whenever it's not the normal schedule, they think they can do whatever the heck they want with it, like either make A period first, then a break, and then maybe an assembly as well before starting B period. 

But nooo... today we have the break and assembly AFTER B period. 

So since I'm a senior, I get the privilege of having A period off, meaning I don't have to show up to school at all until B period. And stupid me assumed that the assembly and break are BEFORE B period, so I ended up showing up a good 10 minutes late to my EXAM. I completed it in half the time that we're given, it wasn't that difficult, but SERIOUSLY. I LOATHE how they handle the schedules in this school.
